Bounsweet

Evolves At 4

Steenee

Evolves At 6

Oblivious

Passive Ability

Reduces the duration of hindrances inflicted on the user by an increased amount.

Queenly Majesty

Passive Ability

When a hindrance is inflicted on Tsareena; decrease the duration of the effect. Using a boosted attack or move grants 1 stack of Queenly Majesty to Tsareena. After gaining 3 stacks, the Queenly Majesty buff is applied to Tsareena for a short time, which allows one of Tsareena's moves to be reused (these uses do not share the same cooldown as the base moves), dealing increased damage and applying an additional effect based on the move used.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, lunging at an opposing Pokémon, damage nearby opposing Pokémon and lowering the Defense of those hit by 20% for 1s.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

130% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

Razor Leaf

Move 1

5.00s Area

The user pelts sharp-edged leaves in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon hit up to 3 times. The critical-hit rate of this move is increased by 15%.

62% Atk + 7 x (Level - 1) + 120

Razor Leaf Upgrade Choices

Triple Axel

7.00s Dash

The user dashes forward with 3 spinning kicks, hitting opposing Pokémon in the area of effect of each kick; increasing the user's auto attack speed for 5s per opposing Pokémon hit (up to 3 times), and increasing the damage of the user's auto attacks and Triple Axel by 8% per opposing Pokémon hit before dealing damage (up to 6 times).

Queenly Majesty Effect: Restores HP per opposing Pokémon hit with each kick.

49% Atk + 3 x (Level - 1) + 60

Rapid Spin

Move 2

7.50s Dash

The user dashes forward and spins, damaging opposing Pokémon in their path and increasing the user's movement speed by 30% for 1.5s when it hits.

113% Atk + 8 x (Level - 1) + 260

Rapid Spin Upgrade Choices

Trop Kick

7.00s Dash

The user dashes forward with a flying kick of tropical origins, damaging opposing Pokémon in the path of the kick and decreasing their Attack by 25% for 1s when it hits. At the same time, a muddy wake is left in the path of the kick, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of the wake (up to 7 times) and decreasing their movement speed by 35% for 1s.

Queenly Majesty Effect: Grants the user a shield for 3s when this move is used.

8.00s Dash

Queen Ascendant

Unite Move

112s 100000 Sure Hit

Unlocks at level 9

Tsareena leaps toward an enemy player and kicks it high into the air before showering it with a series of kicks while airborne, dealing damage to them. The moment Tsareena lands on the ground, recover HP. While airborne, the enemy that is being kicked and Tsareena are not affected by other moves.

49% Atk + 1 x (Level - 1) + 70

196% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 280

70% Atk + 5 x (Level - 1) + 350

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
